c: 13
v: 22
t: "usun gibdaabinaa kee Yallih taaqatal yisbire mara, sinni Rabbih fooca edde gurrusak, salat elle faxxiima innal abah soolisaah keenih necee rizqhik tu yacee mara kinni qellisak ayballuk, meqe taamat uma taama gutqa mara tet dugtankeh, too mari usun akeeral ellecabô dabqay fayla le lon"